[thinking] **Considering application context handling**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about whether the withBean DataSource registration happens after the auto-configuration kicks in. I wonder if ApplicationContextRunner manages these conditions effectively. It's interesting that user configurations could load before the auto-configuration. I also note that the FlywayAutoConfiguration operates under the `FlywayDataSourceCondition` during the ConfigurationPhase.REGISTER_BEAN, so it sees the DataSource bean. This connection seems essential for proper configuration flow.
[thinking] 
